                                DiskCopy

        You can copy a disk by selecting the disk icon, holding down Shift,
then double-clicking on the DiskCopy icon. The copy procedure will follow
the same steps as if you had chosen the DiskCopy from the Pull down menus. 
A requester will notify you when it is time to swap disks.

        The DiskCopy program is used by Copy menu item in the Icons menu.
If you simply double-click on the DiskCopy icon, you will be referred to
Copy menu item.


